380
00:18:12,710 --> 00:18:14,440
Why didn't you call me?

381
00:18:14,580 --> 00:18:16,190
I wanted to call you.

382
00:18:16,190 --> 00:18:17,330
Could I even find you?

383
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,770
Where have you been these days?

384
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:22,640
I went to the hot springs

385
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:24,190
with the girls

386
00:18:24,190 --> 00:18:25,130
from the Tea Guild.

387
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:27,300
If I had known Yunzhu
would be singing here,

388
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:28,530
who'd go to the hot springs?

389
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:34,810
You like listening to Yunzhu sing?

390
00:18:35,390 --> 00:18:36,530
I'll have him

391
00:18:36,740 --> 00:18:38,500
sing a song for you.

392
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:41,990
Just for me?

393
00:18:41,990 --> 00:18:42,930
You want to hear it?

394
00:18:43,630 --> 00:18:44,770
I'll find him right away.

395
00:18:45,230 --> 00:18:46,170
Come on.

