She was called away

409
00:19:17,670 --> 00:19:18,680
by Ms. Luo.

410
00:19:20,190 --> 00:19:21,530
Zhusi called her away?

411
00:19:22,540 --> 00:19:24,120
You've been here for a while.

412
00:19:24,430 --> 00:19:25,440
Is everything okay?

413
00:19:26,990 --> 00:19:28,910
You're so meticulous.

414
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:30,290
Everything's perfect.

415
00:19:32,100 --> 00:19:35,120
I have to thank you and Muyun.

416
00:19:35,430 --> 00:19:36,570
Thank us for what?

417
00:19:36,710 --> 00:19:38,190
That day at dinner...

418
00:19:38,190 --> 00:19:39,500
That man...

419
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:41,400
When Chen was here...

420
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:42,760
Sorry

421
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:45,050
for losing control of myself.

422
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:46,570
I'm sorry.

423
00:19:46,910 --> 00:19:47,990
I know you and Muyun

424
00:19:47,990 --> 00:19:50,300
are both thinking of my best.

425
00:19:50,300 --> 00:19:51,910
You wanted me to find

426
00:19:51,910 --> 00:19:53,120
a good match.

427
00:19:54,190 --> 00:19:55,580
I didn't mean that.

428
00:19:55,580 --> 00:19:56,520
You're overthinking.

429
00:19:57,910 --> 00:19:59,010
She didn't mean that.

430
00:20:00,910 --> 00:20:02,250
Then I was overthinking.

431
00:20:03,150 --> 00:20:04,090
Have some tea.

432
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:05,240
Okay.

433
00:20:08,300 --> 00:20:10,680
Ms. Mai, I invited you today

434
00:20:11,230 --> 00:20:13,570
to discuss something.

435
00:20:14,950 --> 00:20:16,260
We're family.

436
00:20:16,260 --> 00:20:17,810
Tell me what you need.

437
00:20:18,470 --> 00:20:20,360
Alright, I'll say it.

438
00:20:21,390 --> 00:20:22,360
I think

439
00:20:22,870 --> 00:20:24,390
Jing Kan is

440
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:26,120
our only heir after all.

441
00:20:26,710 --> 00:20:28,780
He must continue

442
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:31,840
the family line.

443
00:20:32,630 --> 00:20:33,770
Naturally.

444
00:20:34,870 --> 00:20:35,990
I'll urge them

445
00:20:35,990 --> 00:20:37,440
to have a child asap.

446
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:39,720
Yes.

447
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:43,810
But to be safe,

448
00:20:43,990 --> 00:20:44,930
I think it's better

449
00:20:45,150 --> 00:20:48,010
to take a concubine for Jing Kan.

450
00:20:49,470 --> 00:20:50,410
A concubine?

451
00:20:50,630 --> 00:20:52,330
Yes, a concubine.

452
00:20:53,820 --> 00:20:55,090
There are two girls.

453
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:56,970
Help me decide.

454
00:20:58,020 --> 00:20:59,100
One is

455
00:20:59,100 --> 00:21:00,640
a general's daughter,

456
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:03,680
fiery

457
00:21:04,060 --> 00:21:05,400
and strong-willed.

458
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:07,160
The other

459
00:21:07,780 --> 00:21:10,330
is from a scholarly family,

460
00:21:12,100 --> 00:21:13,840
intelligent and accomplished

461
00:21:14,300 --> 00:21:17,290
in everything.

462
00:21:17,990 --> 00:21:19,020
Ms. Mai,

463
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:20,880
which of these two girls

464
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:22,840
do you think is better?

465
00:21:24,540 --> 00:21:25,600
Actually, I think

466
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:27,730
one wife is fine.

467
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:30,250
Ms. Luo, you've been through it.

468
00:21:30,470 --> 00:21:32,160
Surely, you feel the same.

469
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:36,200
Master Yunzhu has been

470
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:38,330
singing excellent Kun Opera

471
00:21:38,470 --> 00:21:40,250
for us recently.

472
00:21:40,670 --> 00:21:42,640
He's handsome, too.

473
00:21:45,630 --> 00:21:46,570
Ms. Luo,

474
00:21:47,150 --> 00:21:48,640
when I live here,

475
00:21:49,230 --> 00:21:51,330
I'll inevitably have

476
00:21:51,670 --> 00:21:52,810
some social obligations.

477
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:54,440
Well.

478
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:56,100
Ms. Xue

479
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:57,430
likes Yunzhu.

480
00:21:57,430 --> 00:21:59,120
She invited him for a meal.

481
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:00,880
I must help her.

482
00:22:01,380 --> 00:22:02,230
How about this?

483
00:22:02,230 --> 00:22:03,600
I'll talk to Ms. Xue,

484
00:22:03,820 --> 00:22:05,470
and I guarantee Yunzhu

485
00:22:05,470 --> 00:22:06,490
won't come here again.

486
00:22:06,950 --> 00:22:07,890
No, no.

487
00:22:09,150 --> 00:22:11,530
Master Yunzhu must come.

488
00:22:13,950 --> 00:22:15,430
Muyun

489
00:22:15,430 --> 00:22:17,010
is too lonely.

490
00:22:18,060 --> 00:22:20,300
We have to help her find a companion

491
00:22:20,300 --> 00:22:22,500
to take care of her

492
00:22:22,500 --> 00:22:23,640
by her side.

493
00:22:24,470 --> 00:22:25,410
Anyway,

494
00:22:25,870 --> 00:22:27,330
we'll have

495
00:22:27,670 --> 00:22:29,330
a wedding soon.

496
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:32,680
It's either for Jing Kan or Muyun.

497
00:22:33,990 --> 00:22:34,930
Ms. Mai,

498
00:22:35,670 --> 00:22:38,530
who do you think is more urgent?

499
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:54,250
Sixi, Sixi.

500
00:22:55,430 --> 00:22:56,300
You've found yourself

501
00:22:56,300 --> 00:22:57,570
such a good mother-in-law.

502
00:23:00,260 --> 00:23:00,600
Madam,

503
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:02,200
are you really going to play matchmaker

504
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,670
for Ms. Xue and Master Yunzhu?

505
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:06,280
Of course.

506
00:23:06,390 --> 00:23:08,050
Why? Do you have objections?

507
00:23:08,710 --> 00:23:09,650
No.

508
00:23:09,990 --> 00:23:11,680
I just don't think Ms. Xue deserves him.

509
00:23:12,470 --> 00:23:13,410
And you do?

510
00:23:13,910 --> 00:23:14,920
Come on.

511
00:23:15,230 --> 00:23:16,810
I'm just giving advice.

512
00:23:17,470 --> 00:23:19,160
I know what you're thinking.

513
00:23:20,340 --> 00:23:21,280
Think about it.

514
00:23:21,990 --> 00:23:22,930
All these years,

515
00:23:23,260 --> 00:23:24,680
I tried to find you several matches,

516
00:23:24,910 --> 00:23:25,920
but none worked out.

517
00:23:26,230 --> 00:23:28,330
Will Yunzhu like you?

518
00:23:29,430 --> 00:23:31,160
Think about it, okay?

519
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:34,600
I'll never know without trying.

520
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:38,400
This is my wife, Qinxin.

521
00:23:38,630 --> 00:23:40,970
That is Ge Yi's wife, Shiyun.

522
00:23:41,390 --> 00:23:42,340
Pleasure to meet you.

523
00:23:42,340 --> 00:23:43,280
Nice to meet you.

524
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:45,360
We and Jing Kan

525
00:23:45,470 --> 00:23:47,490
were classmates at the school.

526
00:23:48,990 --> 00:23:49,990
Have you shown

527
00:23:49,990 --> 00:23:51,400
your poetry collection to Sixi?

528
00:23:53,150 --> 00:23:54,400
You used to write poems?

529
00:23:55,950 --> 00:23:56,970
That was in the past.

530
00:23:57,190 --> 00:23:58,560
I'll show it when there's a chance.

531
00:24:00,020 --> 00:24:00,910
Today, I brought

532
00:24:00,910 --> 00:24:02,160
Mifangzong Tea with me.

533
00:24:02,500 --> 00:24:03,490
Since everyone's here,

534
00:24:03,870 --> 00:24:04,970
taste it.

535
00:24:05,580 --> 00:24:07,400
I heard it's the new product
from Ruicao Tea.

536
00:24:07,990 --> 00:24:08,870
Qinxin

537
00:24:08,870 --> 00:24:10,010
has been wanting to try it.

538
00:24:10,540 --> 00:24:12,230
The last thing I longed for like this

539
00:24:12,230 --> 00:24:13,400
was Banfang Tea.

540
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:15,600
I'll pour some water for you.

541
00:24:23,500 --> 00:24:24,440
Here.

542
00:24:25,190 --> 00:24:26,130
Come on.

543
00:24:31,150 --> 00:24:32,090
This tea is really good.

544
00:24:33,990 --> 00:24:36,020
The tea soup is milky and smooth,

545
00:24:36,020 --> 00:24:37,090
fragrant at the nose.

546
00:24:37,390 --> 00:24:38,730
This tea is excellent.

547
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:40,100
Right?

548
00:24:40,100 --> 00:24:41,970
I think Mifangzong is richer.

549
00:24:42,150 --> 00:24:43,540
And the spring water here,

550
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:44,810
infused with bamboo fragrance,

551
00:24:45,190 --> 00:24:47,120
makes it even fresher.

552
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:53,240
Indeed.

553
00:24:54,150 --> 00:24:55,200
Here, let me get you more.

554
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:57,500
I think

555
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,500
Sixi is also

556
00:24:58,500 --> 00:25:00,050
a straightforward,

557
00:25:00,230 --> 00:25:01,340
free-spirited girl.

558
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:02,430
Maybe she doesn't like

559
00:25:02,430 --> 00:25:03,570
pretentious elegance like us.

560
00:25:03,950 --> 00:25:05,970
No, a touch of elegance is good.

561
00:25:06,630 --> 00:25:09,490
Why not drink some wine?

562
00:25:10,430 --> 00:25:11,570
Sounds good.

563
00:25:12,990 --> 00:25:14,810
I brought some fine wine.

564
00:25:17,190 --> 00:25:18,680
Moonlit.

565
00:25:19,470 --> 00:25:21,530
This is our family's private reserve.

566
00:25:34,260 --> 00:25:35,310
- Here.
- Come on.

567
00:25:39,910 --> 00:25:41,680
It's rare that we gather today.

568
00:25:41,990 --> 00:25:44,050
Why not drink

569
00:25:44,230 --> 00:25:46,120
with poetry as before?

570
00:25:46,780 --> 00:25:48,400
Great, I'll start.

571
00:25:49,300 --> 00:25:53,580
The waters of the Yellow River
come from the sky.

572
00:25:53,580 --> 00:25:55,910
And rush to the sea.

573
00:25:55,910 --> 00:25:59,250
Facing the mirror,
our parents find their hair gray.

574
00:25:59,470 --> 00:26:01,880
In the blink of an eye, things change.

575
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:04,400
One must enjoy to the fullest
in the prime of life.

576
00:26:06,390 --> 00:26:07,330
Good.

577
00:26:08,430 --> 00:26:11,010
Do not let the cup face the moon empty.

578
00:26:11,390 --> 00:26:13,200
One must be here for a reason.

579
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:16,600
A thousand gold spent always comes back.

580
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:18,710
Let us be merry,
surrounded by lamb and beef.

581
00:26:18,710 --> 00:26:20,530
Let us drink as much as we can.

582
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:21,560
I agree.

583
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,530
Danqiu.

584
00:26:23,340 --> 00:26:24,400
Let us drink.

585
00:26:25,100 --> 00:26:26,430
Do not stop.

586
00:26:26,430 --> 00:26:28,440
I'll sing a song for you.

587
00:26:29,020 --> 00:26:30,810
